Import latest DynastyProcess player IDs

Source: R/1_import_dp.R
dp_playerids.Rd

Fetches a copy of the latest DynastyProcess player IDs csv

dp_playerids()

Value

a tibble of player IDs

See also

https://github.com/DynastyProcess/data

Examples

# \donttest{
dp_playerids()
